Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + Wait' in comparison to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time to 'Accepted + Wait' grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Average time it takes 'Accepted + Wait' to be done after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases where 'Completed + In Call' follows
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total time it takes 'Accepted + Wait' after the execution of 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Wait' in cases leading to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Wait' in variants where 'Accepted + In Progress' occurs before and after
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Accepted + Wait' in comparison to 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait' to the next activity, excluding 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched does not occur

Name: Minimum time it takes 'Accepted + Wait' to be done before 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Wait' to transition to any 'Completed' status activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Average time between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in the context of VINST system usage
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Wait' in the process leading to 'Completed + In Call', reflecting on its impact
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
